    "citationNoticeFull": "The scientific publication on OVIS is currently in progress.<br>Until its release, we recommend citing one of the following sources:<br><p><b>GitHub Repository: OVIS</b> <br> https://github.com/tryovis/ovis </p><p><b>Reference to predecessor project (MOCCA):</b><br><i>Nasseh, D., Schneiderbauer, S., Lange, M., Schweizer, D., Heinemann, V., Belka, C., ... & Fey, T. (2020). Optimizing the analytical value of oncology-related data based on an in-memory analysis layer: Development and assessment of the Munich online comprehensive cancer analysis platform. Journal of Medical Internet Research, 22(4), e16533.</i></p>",
